Introduction

Chaewon is a South Korean singer under M25.

On September 14, 2021, Chaewon was revealed as a contestant on the MBC's survival show "My Teenage Girl". During the finale, she ranked seventh place with 198,915.5 votes, thus becoming the last member of the girl group CLASS:y. CLASS:y made their debut on May 5, 2022 with the mini album "Class Is Over".

On May 14, 2024, Chaewon released her first digital single "Americano on a Rainy Day".
